## Additional Terms for Skills Content

While the code and documentation in this repository are under MIT License,
the skills themselves (the instructional content, patterns, and best practices
documented in SKILL.md files) are provided with the following understanding:

1. **Usage**: You may freely use these skills in personal and commercial projects
